<br>
Mana/wisdom in itself is not as important.  It's not terribly difficult to get your wisdom up to 255+ anyway, so start trading things out.  <br>
<br>
Trade out for what?  <br>
<br>
Well, first... I think it goes without saying, Mana preservation, flowing thought.  Other focuse effects are important.<br>
<br>
HP are VERY important.  Every little bit helps.  When I put on my gear, I double my hp now.  I'm getting close to 2k hp unbuffed, which is pretty good for a non-raiding enchanter I think?  But just being able to take one more hit without getting blood aggro can mean life or death sometimes.<br>
<br>
Also maybe look into something with +channeling.  Channel that heal through and you'll give the tank a lot more time to save you.<br>
<br>
These thing obviously don't help as much in raid situations, but are an incredible benefit in single group hunts.<br>
<br>
Just some ideas<br>
